{"tid":1586573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要］黃絲黑店？！諗清楚先好去！！","createTime":"2019-09-22T04:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T05:21:01.000Z","uid":316284,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"89bbee4b5c1463d9383b1236771057bc04e49da4","tid":1586573,"uid":316284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:30:55.000Z","msg":"有文宣推薦大家支持黃絲鋪頭，但都要小心黑店！！<br />\n<br />\n［以下為朋友親身經歷］<br />\n<br />\n//Quote//<br />\n話說早幾個月前手機突然壞左，開唔到機，經介紹下去左「師傅到手機維修專門店」整機。放低左部機幾日，店員回覆個mon同底板壞左，所以換曬兩樣。過左一排，個mon又死左，只可以display但touch唔到！😑 之後我去左另一間整，發現「師傅到」幫我換嘅係假屏！🤬🤬<br />\n//Unquote//<br />\n<br />\n收幾百蚊換個成本幾十蚊人仔嘅假屏，良心何在？！希望大家小心d呢間鋪頭，幫襯前都要諗清楚！！朋友中左伏唔打算追究，但都想出個post，善意提醒大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n假屏實圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KVogHkg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKVogHkg.jpg&h=580c1125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFB 帖文<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VA4Dbfc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVA4Dbfc.png&h=424098ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAg6ka2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAg6ka2.png&h=98caebb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 朋友整完部機仲有野壞，去鋪頭向店員查詢但店員態度極差，西面加唔覆msg。"},{"pid":"3d63f34935de7d2f19d66d712f35ea8b1d2690e9","tid":1586573,"uid":316284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:38:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b864558391bc578573f0ddead94c690e9547f746","tid":1586573,"uid":316284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:38:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2486bf0df7f1258d748a4cacc470e2e6f2b46246","tid":1586573,"uid":316284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:38:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8398cfa72d75454ba091b84c1c80f4c4944fad4","tid":1586573,"uid":316284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b70786b0c4ff465a1